Document Scanner is an OpenCV project using Python.
We have 2 Python Files, one with main code and another with supporting codes.
In this Project , the Pipeline is :
 1- we scan the picture using webcam or take it from our gallery , I have given a path for the same.
 2-Convert it to Gray Scale
 3- Try to find edges using edge detector
 4- Contour the image
 5- Filter and get the biggest Contour
 6-With the corner points of the Biggest contour , get Warp Perspective of Image.
 7- Apply adaptive THRESHOLDING to get scanned paper feel.
 8-Add functionality of saving the Image in the folder.

There can be issue while installing cv2 package, make sure to use the correct version for opencv-python package.
